#X text 394 44 NOTES \; ------------------------------------------------------------------------- \; - WAVE LOADED SHOULD ALREADY BE NORMALIZED \; - VELOCITY(AMPLITUDE) LEVEL [0:1]. FURTHER AMPLIFICATIONS OUTSIDE OUTLET~ \; - TO KEEP ON A SOUND SEND "NOTE + VELOCITY >0" IT WILL STAY ON SUSTAIN LEVEL UNTIL NOTE OFF ("NOTE+VELOCITY=0") IS SENT \; - IF NEW FREQUENCY OR VELOCITY ARRIVES ON SUSTAIN LEVEL \, NO NEW ATTACK HAPPENS. SOUND EVOLVES PITCH AND AMLITUDE WISE FROM CURRENT STATE ******** THIS PART IS CHANGED. IF NEW MIDI OR VELOCITY ARRIVES \, THE PATCH IS SET TO "STOP THE PREVIOUS CHANNEL WITH A QUICK RAMP AND RESTARTS THE ADSR IN THE NEXT CHANNEL \; - MIDI ON: NOTE NUMBER + VELOCITY (1-127: 0-1): PEAK OF ADSR \; - MIDI OFF: NOTE NUMBER + 0 \; - SHAPE OF ADSR ENVELOPE IS DEFINES INTERNALY AND SAVED. COULD LATER MAKE A DESIGN TO RECEIE THIS FROM A SEQEUNCER AS WELL IF NEEDED., f 75;
